60 dispose of such abandoned property without further notice. If
61 you do not move out by the date and time ordered by the court,
62 the landlord may have you removed by law enforcement and the
63 landlord may remove any personal property remaining on the
64 premises to the curb or an area designated for garbage. The
65 landlord will have no obligation to preserve the personal
66 property upon removal."
67 (c) The notice shall be served on the defendant at
